Wiki markup:
{noformat}{{\_\_CLASS\_\_}}{noformat}
Expected output: (with two underscores on either side and monospaced)
{noformat}__CLASS__{noformat}

Displays correctly when previewed but is then mangled when the document containing it is saved. When the document is retrieved again, that segment has been changed to the following.

Wiki markup:
{noformat}{{\__CLASS_\_}}{noformat}
Actual output: (with one underscore on either side, monospaced, and italicized)
{noformat}_CLASS_{noformat}

